sary-reissue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisStandingOnTheShoulderOfGiants-25th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>宣布了他们的第四张录音室专辑《 Stand of Giants的肩膀》的25周年重新发行。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/oasis-reunion-liam-noel-gallagher-3787549">您必须与之相关：通往绿洲超音速返回的岩石之路</a></strong></li></ul><p>该唱片的新版本将于2月28日星期五到达 - 原始专辑于2000年发行的同一日期。它将在限量版乙烯基上发行，包括Silver LP，以及官方的商店专用蓝色和紫色大理石唱片。</p><p> “站在巨人的肩膀上”在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆（Liam）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）</a>自己的唱片公司Big Brother Recordings Ltd上发行。主打单曲“ Go Let It Out”标记了标签上的第一材料。在Oasis的前英国唱片公司创作记录突然关闭之后，Big Brother于2000年1月推出。</p><p>这张专辑是Oasis的声音中的大胆发展，Noel采取了更广泛，更具实验性的录制方法，转向了现代迷幻岩石影响的风格。</p><p> “……巨人”在英国专辑排行榜中排名第一，仅在第一周就售出了310,000张。现在已通过Double Platinum认证，在美国售出了200,000多份。 </p><figure id="attachment_3835876" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835876" style="width: 628px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835876" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisSOTSOG-reissue-preview-1.jpg" alt="绿洲 - “站在巨人队的肩膀上25周年纪念日重新发行" width="628" height="450" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisSOTSOG-reissue-preview-1.jpg 628w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisSOTSOG-reissue-preview-1-400x287.jpg 400w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835876" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲 - “站在巨人队25周年纪念日的肩膀上。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3835877" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835877" style="width: 634px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835877" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisSOTSOG-reissue-preview-2.jpg" alt="绿洲 - “站在巨人队的肩膀上25周年纪念日重新发行" width="634" height="454" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisSOTSOG-reissue-preview-2.jpg 634w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OasisSOTSOG-reissue-preview-2-400x286.jpg 400w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 634px) 100vw, 634px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835877" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲 - “站在巨人队25周年纪念日的肩膀上。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>该唱片还以单身人士的身份“谁感到爱”？“这一切都出错了？”和“周日早上打电话”，以及灌木丛中的歌曲“ Fuckin”和“ Gas Panic！”。</p><p>该专辑的第一张单曲“ Go Let It Out”的新抒情视频最初于25年前（2月7日）发行，该视频将于格林尼治标准时间下午4点在YouTube上。<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mIK9nx4mL2E" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问YouTube首映页面</a>。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://oasismusic.lnk.to/sotsog25PR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>预订Oasis的25周年纪念版。请参阅下面的跟踪列表，然后查看上面的预览图像。</p><p> <strong>1。“在灌木丛中&#39;他妈的&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。“去放开”</strong><br /> <strong>3。“谁感觉到爱？”</strong><br /> <strong>4。“把钱放在你的嘴里”</strong><br /> <strong>5。“小詹姆斯”</strong><br /> <strong>6。“恐慌！”</strong><br /> <strong>7。“这一切都在哪里出错？”</strong><br /> <strong>8。“周日早上电话”</strong><br /> <strong>9。&#39;我可以看到骗子&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>10。“滚动”</strong></p><p>该新闻是在乐队宣布汇编专辑“ Time Flies…1994  -  2009年”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2025-full-list-releases-vinyl-3835631">《唱片店Day》 2025年</a>的15周年纪念版之后发布的。去年，他们发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">30周年的开创性首次亮相“绝对也许”</a> 。这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-to-celebrate-25-years-of-whats-the-story-morning-glory-with-special-vinyl-reissue-2744484#">在重新发行的标记25年的“（故事）早晨的荣耀？”</a> 2020年。</p><p> Oasis将于今年开始进行大规模的复出巡回演出，这是他们自2009年以来的第一场现场表演。备受期待的跋涉将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">今年夏天在英国和爱尔兰举行的一场体育场演出</a>开始，随后是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">一系列的日期北美</a>。</p><p>然后，该小组将在9月下旬<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">在伦敦的温布利体育场举行两次额外演出</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">前往韩国和日本</a>。在今年11月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">在南美举行的广泛巡回演出</a>之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">，澳大利亚举行了更多音乐会</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?start=2&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>对于英国和爱尔兰的腿， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-richard-ashcroft-as-special-guest-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3804758">绿洲将得到理查德·阿什克罗夫特（Richard Ashcroft）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cast-oasis-interview-support-tour-liam-noel-gallagher-richard-ashcroft-3807494#:~:text=Cast%20frontman%20John%20Power%20has,positive%20vibe%E2%80%9D%20from%20all%20involved.">演员</a>的支持。北美的日期<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cage-the-elephant-interview-oasis-north-american-tour-support-uk-shows-manchester-3814419">以笼子为开幕法</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-responds-to-rumours-about-zak-starkey-rejoining-oasis-3831341">肖恩·莱德（Shaun Ryder）最近回应了谣传扎克·斯塔基（Zak Starkey）将重新加入绿洲的聚会表演</a>。同时，加拉格尔（Gallagher <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-leaked-oasis-reunion-tour-setlist-3827166">）对“泄漏”的绿洲复出巡回赛套装作出了回应</a>。</p><p>同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-liam-gallagher-raekwon-and-ghostface-killah-star-in-new-film-celebrating-200th-anniversary-of-clarks-shoes-3835110">利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）出演了一部新的简短纪录片，庆祝了200年的鞋品牌克拉克斯（Clarks）</a> 。他将于今年与该公司发布第二次合作。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-25th-anniversary-standing-on-the-shoulder-of-giants-reissue-3835860">绿洲后宣布25周年“站在巨人的肩膀上”重新发行，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
莎拉·米歇尔·盖拉（Sarah Michelle Gellar）证实了“巴菲”的复兴：“这将适合你” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sarah-michelle-gellar-confirms-buffy-revival-this-will-be-for-you-3835882?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sarah-michelle-gellar-确认 - 巴菲 - 重生 - 这将成为您的事Tom SkinnerFri, 07 Feb 2025 08:28:14 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3835882 <p><img width="2000" height="1275" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎拉·米歇尔·盖尔（Sarah Michelle Gellar）从1997年至2003年出演了“巴菲”。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-400x255.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-800x510.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-696x444.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-1392x887.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-1068x681.jpeg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演员详细介绍了使演出脱离地面的“漫长过程”，但她说她和球队“在那里的道路上”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sarah-michelle-gellar-confirms-buffy-revival-this-will-be-for-you-3835882">萨拉·米歇尔·盖拉（Sarah Michelle Gellar）的帖子证实了“ Buffy”的复兴：“这将为您为您”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1275" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莎拉·米歇尔·盖尔（Sarah Michelle Gellar）从1997年至2003年出演了“巴菲”。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-400x255.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-800x510.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-696x444.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-1392x887.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-in-Buffy-1068x681.jpeg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>莎拉·米歇尔·盖拉尔（Sarah Michelle Gellar）证实，在报道说该节目将返回之后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/buffy-the-vampire-slayer"><em>吸血鬼杀手巴菲（Buffy）</em></a>的复兴正在进行中。</p><p>本周早些时候， <a href="https://variety.com/2025/tv/news/buffy-the-vampire-slayer-revival-hulu-sarah-michelle-gellar-pilot-1236291559/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道说，Gellar在续集系列中扮演Buffy Summers的角色，最初是从1997年到2003年的热门超自然戏剧。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/buffy-the-vampire-slayer-best-episodes-2008804"><em>Buffy</em> Turn 20：节目最佳情节的倒计时</a></strong></li></ul><p>该媒体声称，尚未提出的表演将重点放在一个新的杀手上，而Gellar出现了反复出现的角色，而不是扮演主角。据说Gellar将与Gail Berman一起担任执行制片人。</p><p> <em>Variety</em>报道说，诺拉（Nora）和莉拉·扎克曼（Lila Zuckerman）依附于写作，表演和执行产品。它说，以<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Oscars+NME&amp;sca_esv=81490bff7710e63a&amp;sxsrf=AHTn8zpRHtJE9JzV8z2cWAnZLwxP2cUvIg%3A1738915799835&amp;ei=17-lZ-_WMviEhbIPop3TmQ4&amp;ved=0ahUKEwivnqyUjrGLAxV4QkEAHaLONOMQ4dUDCBA&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=Oscars+NME&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCk9zY2FycyBOTUUyBxAAGIAEGA0yBxAAGIAEGA0yBxAAGIAEGA0yBhAAGA0YHjIGEAAYDRgeMgYQABgNGB4yCBAAGAUYDRgeMggQABgFGA0YHjIIEAAYBRgNGB4yCBAAGAgYDRgeSO0FUABYAHAAeAGQAQCYAc8BoAGTA6oBBTEuMS4xuAEDyAEA-AEBmAIDoAKKBJgDAOIDBRIBMSBAkgcFMS4wLjKgB6kV&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp">奥斯卡</a><em>奖</em>（2020年）而闻名的ChloéZhao将担任导演和执行制片人。</p><p>现在，Gellar在社交媒体上的一篇文章中回应了新闻。她确认了自己参与该项目的参与，但没有透露这是重新启动还是续集。</p><p> “所以……您本周可能已经听到了一些消息，但是我意识到您没有收到我的来信，”这位演员开始回想起三年前伯曼的电话。</p><p>盖拉尔写道：“她告诉我，她希望我与ChloéZhao坐下来，听听她的潜在<em>Buffy</em> Revival。”</p><p> “我被克洛埃（Chloé）甚至知道我是谁感到震惊，但是，正如我一直这样做的那样，我告诉盖尔（Gail），我只是没有看到演出再次存在的方法。我们一直对此保持一致，但是这次我听到了她的声音不同。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFvUywyvMy2/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.