/knocked-loose">敲门声则被</a>提名，而Carpenter（也在奖项中也获得了奖项）获得了多个奖项的提名。</p><p> Poppy最终输给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a> ，而Carpenter获得了最佳流行音乐表演和最佳流行声乐专辑的奖项 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3833854">您可以在这里看到Grammys 2025获奖者的完整列表</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3835823" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835823" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835823" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sabrina-carpenter-poppy-2019@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835823" class="wp-caption-text"> Sabrina Carpenter和Poppy在2019年。信用：DCP的Kevin Mazur/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>自格莱美岛以来，罂粟一直是一个<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spiritboxs-courtney-laplante-pretends-to-be-poppy-for-grammys-interview-after-awkward-case-of-mistaken-identity-3833962">有趣的身份案例的</a>头条新闻。在红地毯上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">《精神盒》的金属音乐家考特尼·拉普兰特（Courtney Laplante）</a>被记者误认同为罂粟，并接受了拉普兰特（Laplante）的采访，拉普兰特（Laplante）被放在现场，不得不回答针对罂粟的问题。</p><p>拉普兰特（Laplante）决定出现尴尬的错误，回答好像她是罂粟一样。在给面试官一个混乱的外观之后，拉普兰特回答：“我是罂粟，我真的很高兴在这里被敲定的人提名。我希望是我（赢）或Spiritbox和Courtney。” </p><figure id="attachment_3578351" aria-describedby="caption-